snippet.title: Aircraft Sketch Shooter - Another Trailer
snippet.description:
Aircraft Sketch Shooter Trailer


An Ink Style Arcade Action Shooter, Choose your Aircraft, your Graphic Style, play through Unique Designed Levels and go for Highscore Races in an Endless Generated Level.
